   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-c" mid="15" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Why did you buy those things suddenly?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Yes, boxes of comb and gum, snacks, cushions for Hounds.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-d" mid="17" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Is it enough to prove though?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>The Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals will be coming soon. I have to show them how much I care and love my Hounds, don't I?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-d" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-e" mid="20" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Berlin holds his head with both hands and looks rather in pain)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="18"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>I don't think so. I need to try and show them but who can guarantee success?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-e" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-f" mid="22" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Shall I?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Can't even have someone to vouch for me with money!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-f" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-g" mid="24" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Huh? Is there this kinda rumor spreading around?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Everyone at Saint Haven heard the rumor that you and I are close. They will think that you lie to take my side, so your vouch won't be so helpful.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-g" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-h" mid="26" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Something rushes to Berlin's mind.)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="25"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Where can I find someone to vouch for me? Unless those Hounds learn to speak suddenly and prove that they're well fed, sleep well... wait a moment.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-h" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-i" mid="28" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>Talking Hounds?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>A Talking Hound! Now I remember my cousin Borin at Mana Ridge told me there are talking Hounds on the chimney of the forge.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-i" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-j" mid="30" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="29"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Yes, it's unbelievable and strange that the Hound speaks. But a drowning man will clutch at any straw. I'll take any chances.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-j" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-k" mid="32" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>What's that?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="31"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>Go to Mana Ridge now and find out whether there is a talking Hound. If you find it, persuade him to sign this.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-k" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n091_trader_bellin-accepting-l" mid="34" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(What shall I do?)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="33"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Berlin$<BR>This is{item:400198}. It's not signed yet. If I get the credible Hound's signature, the Society for the Prevention of Cruelty to Animals may change their minds.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
